003892BF.Desc: {c_important}Twisting Blades{/c} orbit for a short time after they return to you, dealing {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} of {c_important}Twisting Blades'{/c} return damage per hit. Based on the distance the blades returned, the orbit damage increases up to {c_random}[Affix_Value_1 * 2|%|]{/c} of the return damage.
